<paragraph id="732E7721FFC6FFC5FEAA2710DEB7F9CA" blockId="17.[264,1324,284,1870]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">
<emphasis id="41E5AB33FFC6FFC5FEAA2710DBA5F9A1" bold="true" box="[312,427,1563,1589]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Variation</emphasis>
. Little variation has been noted. In some males the mid and hind tibiae are lighter colored than as described. The pile varies from pure white to pale yellow.
</paragraph>
